videos.description: After a few outlets passes, Kenny Williams finds Garrison Brooks for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Tar Heels' hustle leads  to nice bucket

videos.description: Seventh Woods crosses Spencer Haldeman to the left, then steps back and hits the jumper.
videos.headline: Tar Heels' Woods puts defender on skates

videos.description: Theo Pinson penetrates and drops it off to Sterling Manley for the two-hand slam.
videos.headline: Tar Heels rolling after Manley jam

videos.description: Theo Pinson swings it over to Kenny Williams and he knocks down a deep 3-pointer to put the Heels up by 23.
videos.headline: Tar Heels Williams hitting from deep

videos.description: Luke Maye led the Tar Heels with 26-points. They were able to play fast paced without their leader Joel Berry ll.
videos.headline: Tar Heels dominate in 1st game of the season 86-69
